  <p>When your pet needs surgery, you want a team you can trust. All About Pets Veterinary Hospital provides safe, effective surgical care with attentive monitoring before, during, and after every procedure.</p>

  <h2>Our Pet Surgery Services</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Spay and neuter procedures</li>
    <li>Soft tissue surgery</li>
    <li>Mass and tumor removal</li>
    <li>Wound repair</li>
    <li>Foreign body removal</li>
    <li>Other routine surgical procedures</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>What to Expect</h3>
  <p>Before any procedure, we conduct a thorough pre-surgical assessment, including bloodwork and other diagnostics as needed, to make sure your pet is a good candidate for anesthesia and surgery.</p>
  <p>During surgery, your pet is monitored continuously. After the procedure, we provide clear post-operative instructions and follow-up care to support a smooth recovery.</p>

  <h3>Pain Management</h3>
  <p>We take post-surgical pain management seriously. Every surgical patient receives an individualized pain management plan to keep them comfortable during recovery.</p>

  <p>Contact us if your pet needs a surgical consultation.</p>
